    "description": "Are you a skilled Sales Manager looking for your next big career move? Anarock Property Consultants in Kochi offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Anarock Property Consultants:\nAnarock Property Consultants is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Anarock Property Consultants!",
